{"tid":944842,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大愈少朋友","createTime":"2018-12-17T12:15:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T13:01:44.000Z","uid":102335,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59e8d3ee5373a33ef3de3bdbb2c3235dcfc39378","tid":944842,"uid":102335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:15:57.000Z","msg":"見到隔離開左個25歲愈來愈少朋友好感觸<br />\n好記得以前一班朋友出黎玩 出黎食飯<br />\n唔開心既時候一班人出黎玩就好快唔記得唔開心既野<br />\n以家25歲後 5隻手指數得哂既朋友<br />\n唔開心都唔知講唔講好 又怕人唔想聽<br />\n約食飯又難約 一個月見到一次已經好好<br />\n見到人地好多朋友成日post相好開心<br />\n25歲後身邊好多結哂婚 有小朋友<br />\n愈講愈灰 真係好懷念以前一大班朋友成日見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c1b08b481ed009e7ce638db9988fae15ab0215","tid":944842,"uid":41475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:16:41.000Z","msg":"人愈大都愈小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad7e89077a14556a2e98b62c98c4e8ac41e1294a","tid":944842,"uid":44626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:29:42.000Z","msg":"I know that feel bro..."},{"pid":"b9f5a58469eb351236071b3ab970ba45e9ab7c3e","tid":944842,"uid":102335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T12:40:47.000Z","msg":"冇人圍下爐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc34b706c4f930c25a3333d66a78f6773093620","tid":944842,"uid":176890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-17T13:01:44.000Z","msg":"我17歲中學都自己一個食飯<br />\n日日放學返屋企上舊登<br />\n家下日日放工上連登<br />\n唔覺有咩問題"}]}